{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_48","type":"agent_message","text":"I have enough context to plan the fix. The work splits into three parts:\n1. Separate the canonical readable manuscript from downloadable story exports in hydration/snapshot state, so DOCX generation doesn’t break the finalize reader.\n2. Add an explicit backend export trigger that generates or refreshes the DOCX asset against the latest accepted `story_text` asset and returns discoverable asset metadata.\n3. Expand API/service tests around regeneration, snapshot behavior, and endpoint behavior, then run targeted backend verification and commit the checkpoint."}}
